        <div class="activityboxtext">
            <h3 class="activityboxh3">Invited to Disability Center</h3>
            <div class="activityboxp">
            On 11 November 2019, Hana's Garden had been invited to Goodluck Disability Center.<br /><br />
            We reached the disability center at 11 a.m. After we reached the disability center, there was a lot of disabled welcome us outside the gate. They danced and sing on the stage to us.<br /><br />
            At 12.30 p.m, we started to teach them the knowledge of flowers. This activity ended at 5.00p.m. Before we leaved, they cooked their own-made dishes to us to thanks our teaching. We leaved at 6.00p.m.<br /><br />
            The reason we went to there is because we had been invited to teach disabled about some knowledge about flower and how to decorate with some flower.<br /><br />
            We accepted this invitation is because we want to help these disabled to get some skills so they may use these skills to earn money in the future.<br /><br />
            We felt very happy because we had helped some disabled for their better life.
            </div>
        </div>
    </blockquote>
    
    <blockquote class="activitybox">
        <img src="bazaar.jpg" alt="Bazaar" style="width: 40%;" />
        <div class="activityboxtext">
            <h3 class="activityboxh3">Joined bazaar to help poor family</h3>
            <div class="activityboxp">
                On 12 & 13 January 2020, Hana's Garden had join a bazaar named "Bazaar Before Chinese New Year" located in Georgetown.<br /><br />
                We reached the event hall at 7.00 a.m. and we prepared for the bazaar. The bazaar is started at 8.00a.m. and ended at 9.00p.m.<br /><br />
                We sold flower that had been discount to earn more money. The income that earn from the bazaar has been donated to some poor family for their better life.<br /><br />
                We joined the bazaar is because we want to help some poor family for their future and they can use these monry for food, education and other.<br /><br />
                We felt very happy because we had helped some poor family for their better life.
            </div>
        </div>
